Univen Campus Navigator

Univen Campus Navigator is a lightweight, web-based assistant designed to help students navigate the University of Venda campus with ease. It features an intuitive chat-style interface that allows users to quickly find directions, locate buildings, and access general campus navigation support within a clean and modern environment.

Features
Interactive chat-based navigation system
Responsive split-view layout for improved usability
Smooth animations with a modern dark-themed design
Scalable structure ready for backend or AI integration
Mobile-friendly and fully browser-based (no installation required)

Technologies Used
HTML5 – structure and content
CSS3 – styling, Flexbox layout, and animations
JavaScript (optional) – for chat logic and future enhancements
Getting Started
Download or clone the project files
Open the index.html file in any modern web browser
Start interacting with the navigator through the chat interface

Future Improvements
Integration with live campus maps
AI-powered navigation responses
Real-time building and route search
Backend API connectivity for dynamic data

